data.description: Ready now! New construction luxury town homes in the heart of Great Bridge. 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms with open floor plans. 1 car attached garage with 2 car driveway pad. 9' ceilings on the 1st & 2nd floors. Standard features include Cortec floors on the 1st level, granite counters in the gourmet kitchen & master bathroom. Soft close cabinets throughout. Double trash pull out cabinet in the kitchen, crown molding in the master bedroom. Craftsman style garage door with opener. Covered from porch. We have 2 floor plans left. Condo fee includes ground maintenance, trash pickup & dog park. So much to see we can't list it all. Closing cost assistance with use of our builder's preferred lenders. Military - $99 EMD. Summit construction has over 35 years of local building.  Model home open 12-5pm daily & closed on Wednesday. Call or text for showings. Ask about our move-in freebie special!!
